Captain Khanyisile Zwane, said an unknown man stole 100 metres of electric cable valued at approximately R6 000 from Laerskool Middelburg. The incident happened at around 21:15 on Tuesday 13 October. Anyone with information that can lead to an arrest, please contact the Middelburg Police on 013 249 1611/1600. To watch the video, click on the link below: https://vimeo.com/468119714 